data.description: Situated on 1.12 acres, this exceptional property boasts a fenced, cross-fenced, and gated. Inside, you'll find fantastic guest room separation, an open kitchen and dining area, and a Primary ensuite with a soothing garden tub. The home also features a spacious laundry/mudroom for added convenience. With additional amenities such as a storage building, this property ensures practicality and functionality. The U-shaped driveway makes trailer maneuvering a breeze. Located near public land, it offers ample riding opportunities and access to all that Crooked River Ranch has to offer
